==Ancient Greek==

===Pronunciation===
*διαλογίζομαι / dialogizomai / dee-al-og-id'-zom-ahee

===Etymology===
*From [[διά]] {{GG|1223}} and [[λογίζομαι]] {{GG|3049}}; to reckon thoroughly, that is, (generally) to deliberate (by reflection or discussion): 

===Verb===
'''διαλογίζομαι'''

# cast in mind, consider, dispute, muse, reason, [[think]].

